            "title": "盤中速報 - 集中市場加權指數上漲738.23點至37697.03點，漲幅2%",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間21日09:09，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲738.23點（或2%），暫報37697.03點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：+4.23%</li><li>近 1 月：+10.18%</li><li>近 3 月：+16.37%</li><li>近 6 月：+33.48%</li><li>今年以來：+27.6%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>Flash模組概念領漲+4.44%。其中    永崴投控(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3712:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3712\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3712-TW</a>)            上漲        9.91%            ;        宇瞻(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8271:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8271\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8271-TW</a>)            上漲        9.9%            ;        威剛(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3260:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3260\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3260-TW</a>)            上漲        4.47%    。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>植物工廠概念領漲+4.26%。其中    金寶(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2312:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2312\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2312-TW</a>)            上漲        9.92%            ;        連展投控(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3710:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3710\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3710-TW</a>)            上漲        6.38%            ;        欣興(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3037:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3037\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3037-TW</a>)            上漲        4.72%    。</p></section></main>",
